{
  "stem": "13382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because my father was born in Hungary, but while he was in Czechoslovakia it was advantage for him to he become Czechoslavakian--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--citizen-- that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he resigned his Hungarian citizenship and became a Czechoslovakian citizen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow-- I mean, they knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They found out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They started to pester us, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's-- I saw the end-- even when--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Fil'akovo, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was sort of a-- you are such a Hungarian, and you give up your sort of-- because not every Hungarian Czechoslovakian gave up their Hungarian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they'd been working with father and saw a house, an apartment house, going up and for sale.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Budapest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I practically dragged my father in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I says, father, let's go and have a look-- maybe just for-- for out of interest what it is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so the owner of that house, who was building, was a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they already contact her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said to father, we've got to come up to live in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the rent was extremely high, because it was a modern apartment with every facility, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So from there on, it never stopped-- Budapest, Budapest, Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We've got to go to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So finally-- I mean, it wasn't so difficult, I suppose, to agree.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We sold the house in Fil'akovo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, it has a lot to do with-- with going to Budapest that a-- I mean, the shop was already closed-- that we had an offer--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to buy the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A fellow came in, and sort of he wanted to buy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He saw this house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, it was in a good-- good position.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we sold it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that-- and we rented the place in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
